      <hedline>
        <hl1>No More Mr. Nice Guy</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Mike Kondek letter on Stephen S Hall's June 18 The Way We Live Now column offers suggestions on what Lyndon and Lady Bird Johnson and were thinking in photo</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>What a great picture of J.F.K. and L.B.J. It looks as if Lyndon is thinking about holding up a different finger to someone who is probably accusing him of selling out to the Eastern establishment. And Lady Bird is wishing, Get me out of here.</p>
        <p>Mike Kondek  Bloomfield Hills, Mich.</p>
      </block>
